name: The Molten Chocolate Dress
description:
Size: Small

This brown velvet dress is a dream. Get all Lana about it and wear a flower crown to a show or wear out to a romantic evening with your guy.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Twiggy Brady
description:
Size: Small

This baby doll dress gives off the innocence of Cindy Brady but the confidence of a supermodel like Twiggy! Between white, green and blue this short cut dress is givin' off all kinds of vintage studio 54 vibes.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Kill Fringe Vest
description:
The Kill Fringe Vest

Size: Small

This short vest is diluted gray with some serious velvety black fringe hangin onto it. Whether you’re takin a ride on your boyfriend’s harley or goin for a walk in the park this vest aint no ordinary piece.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Daisy Witch
description:
Size: Small

This dress is for when you’re feelin a little naughty and a little nice. The top piece is a cream colored blouse covered in mesh. The bottom is a billowy witch like black skirt that shows you’re not all fun and games. Rock this with some combats and take the day by storm.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Hobo Fairy
description:
Size: Medium

The Hobo Fairy is seriously magical. This fairy is beautiful, but doesn’t quite know where she belongs. Blue with some glittery flowers shows us her beauty but the ragged ends show us her edge!

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Tiger Lily
description:
Size: Medium

This tan blouse is netted on the sleeves and it’s base is entirely suede! Let out your inner Pocohonatas and let it riiiiiiiiiiiide! 

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Goldilocks Croptop
description:
Size: Medium

This gold glittery sweater crop top is perfect for night or day! Wear it to school or wear it out to your family dinner for ma’s birthday. This is sure to add a little shine to any outfit.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: Little Miss Muffet
description:
Size: Medium

This cream colored sweater has some elegant pearl action going down each shoulder with some more pearls across the top with a clean blossom bottom to give it that 80's flair. Have tea with the queen or lunch with your friends in this baby.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: Love Me Down
description:
Size: Large

The Love Me Down is actually DKNY and an alternative twist when it comes to sweaters. Sleeveless with a bulky neck it goes against all rhyme and reason but makes perfect sense. Get down in this anytime!

 (Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Squiggle Vision Sweater
description:
Size: Medium

This black felt sweater has some gold glitter squiggles and gems following right along! Show your inner glamour whore with this fun top.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: Olive You Dress
description:
Size: Medium

This velvety olive green dress with a slit down the sides is beggin' for you take it out for a more swanky night out. Pair it with some creeper heels or grunge it out with some combats, this dress can be whatever you want it to be!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Gold Digger
description:
Size: Small

Now we aint sayin she’s a gold digger….well actually we are. This gray sweater exudes Kanye’s superior attitude toward life and we DIG it! The upper portion of the sweater has some black leather action going on with gold buttons circling the top.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: Metallic Mountain Girl
description:
Size: Large

This puffy metallic blueish green jacket is sure to keep you warm this winter. It’s got plenty of pockets and zipper enclosures so you don’t gotta carry a bag to weigh you down even more! Also included is a built in belt to cinch the waist and add a little femininity to the mix. ;)

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: Oversized Jem Junkie
description:
Size: Extra Large

This over sized jean jacket is seriously one of a kind. It’s emblazoned with all kinds of gems, fringe and lace going down one side and up the back, while the other side is just plain denim. We really think any body type can rock this, it's going to look gigantic on anyone and we think that’s why we love it so much, bag lady!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: Fuck Math
description:
Size: Medium

Fuck math, seriously. Ever sit in class and feel like this sweater…all these symbols and numbers, but what do they mean?! We feel ya. This black sweater with a velvety feel and colored symbols looks like an 80's textbook without the required reading.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: FlowerChild
description:
Size: Medium

Yoko and Lennon’s daughter is actually this sweater. Kick it back to the old school 60's and give off some seriously positive vibes in this flower power sweater!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: Santa's Little Bitch
description:
Size: Small

This red sweater has some even lighter red fuzzy stripes going down it with glitter too! Let Santa know that you might not have been good, but you have been fabulous and that’s what matters most!

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Shewolf
description:
Size: Medium

This sweater is a one of a kind find. Furry on the top in majestic black while the bottom has some metallic undertones within the knit. Roar!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Sultry Slayer Dress
description:
Size: Medium

This black velvet dress with gold buttons is channeling Nancy from the Craft way back to the 90s! There’s a cinch waist rope to make it as tight or loose as you may need making it perf for most body types. Cast a spell on anyone that walks your way in this number.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Sheer Drape Dress
description:
Size: Medium

This sheer, black dress can be utilized for any function. Dress it down with some boots and a cardigan if you’re feelin like Lydia Deetz. Dress it up with some heels if you’re feeling a little more Victoria Beckham.

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Golden Rose Road Shirt
description:
Size: Medium

Sheer black, with gold roses poppin' out at ya! Dress this up with some metallic heels, maybe some darker lips and give off some serious Riri vibes. Perfect for a date night or girls night out!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Morticia Reaper Dress
description:
Size: Large

This black, ribbed, sweater-like dress gives an air of contemporary goth that can be worn anywhere. Show you’re all about business at the office or deck it out in some bling for a cool night out.

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: Paint The Roses Gold
description:
Size: Medium

This velvety black sweater has little gold roses around the neck to give this piece a little shine. Even if you’re having a gloomy kind of day, don’t worry the roses are so small, someone would have to get all up in your biz to see em! This is listed as a medium to be safe, but it could totally be a dress for a tiny chick too!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Blue Bedrock Blouse
description:
Size: Large

This sheer royal blue blouse is emblazoned with some flowers and gray stone undertones that remind us of Bedrock, or maybe even something Peggy Bundy would lounge on the couch with! It’s complete with some stretchy black bands at the waist and arms to serve all body types too!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Holey Moley Sweater
description:
Size: Extra Large

This earth toned cardigan type sweater is weaved with a bunch a’ intricate holes! You don’t gotta cover your whole outfit to keep warm right? 

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Back To Blossom Blouse
description:
Size: Large

This denim long sleeve shirt with printed flowers on it totally reminds us of the 90s sitcom Blossom! This top is effortless and can be worn with a messy bun, black leggings and combat boots.

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The GEMometry Blouse
description:
Size: Large

Don’t you wish geometry class would be a little more fun if all the shapes were shiny, glitzy little trinkets? We sure do! This red button down has a jammed out heart at the top, a blue diamond and a triangle.

(Model pictured is 5’10)

name: The Sherbert Turtleneck
description:
Size: Extra Large

This is the perfect comfy sweater to grab a coffee in and enjoy the crisp autumn air. It is black with white, orange and pink undertones. It’s over sized so anyone can pair it with some leggings, take a walk to Starbucks and Tumblr your life away on their free wifi!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: Black Baby Spice
description:
Size: Small

The Black Baby Spice is a dress with overall type straps and the all over material is like a sweater! Comfortable and cute, if you want to stay true to Baby, we recommend some platforms and knee highs but you can give it a more alternative look like our model did with some boots!

(Model pictured is 5’11)

name: The Sheer Horowitz
description:
Size: Large

This cream button down blouse reminds us of something Cher from Clueless would don walkin' down Rodeo Drive. The buttons are little rhinestone flowers and the sheer cream top is overlaid with some lacey gothic print style!

(Model pictured is 5’10)
